<h2>PRIVACY POLICY</h2>
<p>IMP  Pty Ltd. (&quot;<strong>MYTCG</strong>&quot;) values the privacy of our customers,  users, and others who use the mobile phone application, www.myTCG.net, and  other web sites, services, and content owned or operated by  MYTCG and the MYTCG service are committed to  protecting your privacy. This Privacy Notice details important  information regarding the use and disclosure of User information collected  through the MYTCG Services. MYTCG provides this Privacy Notice to help you make  an informed decision about whether to use or continue using the MYTCG Services. By accessing the Website or the  Service, you are consenting to the information collection and use practices  described in this privacy statement.</p>
