<p>MYTCG uses your personally  identifiable and certain non-personally-identifiable information (such as  anonymous log file information) to track and analyze User preferences and  trends in order to improve the quality and design of the MYTCG Services and to  create new features, promotions, functionality, and services.</p>
<p>We  may use your Personal Information to provide you with important information  about the product or service that you are using, including updates and  notifications. Additionally, with your permission, we may send you information  about other products and services related to the Services, and/or share  information with MYTCG’s subsidiaries, affiliates and/or partners so they may  send you information about their products and services.</p>
<p>If you use the Backup &amp; Sync  feature of the MYTCG Services, MYTCG will store the backup data you provide. If  you delete backup data, we will retain that information for a short amount of  time to enable recovery in the event of accidental deletion. We also store  backup data for a reasonable amount of time after you close your account to allow  recovery if you reactivate your account.</p>
<p>We  might merge Services visitation data with anonymous demographic information for  research purposes, and we may use this information in aggregate to provide more  relevant content.</p>
<p>If you have use the MYTCG Services  with a mobile phone number and device, then MYTCG may send text messages to  your phone to communicate with your device and to provide download links.</p>
<p>When  you sign up for a newsletter or agree to receive promotional email, we may use  customized links or similar technologies to track e-mail links that you click.  We may associate that information with your Personal Information in order to  provide you more focused email communications or purchase information. Each  email communication includes an unsubscribe link allowing you to stop delivery  of that type of communication.</p>
<p>If you email MYTCG for support or  otherwise, or fill out a survey, we will retain that information to provide you  support and to improve the MYTCG Service.</p>
<p>We  might occasionally hire other companies to provide limited services on our  behalf. We shall only provide those companies the Personal Information needed  for them to effectively and efficiently deliver the service.</p>
<p>We  may disclose personal information if required to do so by law or in the good  faith belief that such action is necessary to (a) conform to the edicts of the  law or comply with legal process served on MYTCG or the Services; (b) protect  and defend the rights or property of MYTCG and the Services (as well as other MYTCG  &quot;family Services&quot;, if applicable); or (c) act in urgent circumstances  to protect the personal safety of MYTCG employees or agents, users of MYTCG  products or services, or members of the public.</p>
<p>Personal  Information collected on the Services may be stored and processed in the any  country in which MYTCG or its affiliates, subsidiaries or agents maintain  facilities, and by using the Services, you hereby give your consent to any such  transfer of Personal Information outside your country.</p>
